    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering 333 hp with exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from recent subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver-centric history, the mechanical integrity is robust, with a double VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced. This is a balanced, high-performance machine with a linear power band and an iconic exhaust note, ideal for the purist seeking mechanical soundess over a garage queen.",
