      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example has been maintained with technical rigor: the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan seals and a cryo-treated hub, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with welded plates to ensure torsional rigidity. The chassis benefits from a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Powerflex bushings and Bilstein dampers. It retains the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and valve clearances are within spec. A robust, mechanically sorted platform for the purist.",
